mxalloy third-party notices
===========================

mxalloy is Apache-2.0 licensed. Some model-family implementation code has additional
third-party provenance obligations:

diffusers / transformers
------------------------

The Z-Image transformer under `mxdiffusers/zimage` and the SDXL family under
`mxdiffusers/sdxl` (UNet, CLIP text encoders, AutoencoderKL decoder, Euler scheduler) are
independent MLX reimplementations derived from the Hugging Face `diffusers` and
`transformers` reference implementations.

Upstream: https://github.com/huggingface/diffusers, https://github.com/huggingface/transformers
Copyright (c) The HuggingFace Team. Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0
(http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0). There is no diffusers runtime dependency.

mflux
-----

The FLUX family under `mxdiffusers/flux` was developed as a close MLX port of, and verified
against, mflux. There is no mflux runtime dependency, but while this implementation retains
that port lineage, keep the following MIT notice with distributions of mxalloy/mxdiffusers.

Upstream: https://github.com/filipstrand/mflux

